Verizon,Wireless,provides,authorized,application,developers,with,a,network,based,Messaging,API,service,to,offer,interactive,services,to,our,customers,using,MO,and,MT,messaging,Authorized,application,developers,may,act,as,integration,points,supporting,Verizon,Wireless,with,interactive,messaging,including,television,voting,info,on,demand,real,time,stock,quotes,and,other,premium,content,services,The,API,uses,both,REST,and,SOAP,protocol